bilingual.source: This paper introduces random structural parameters into the stochastic structural analysis.

bilingual.source: Identification of structural damage is always a topic in structural engineering domain.

bilingual.source: How to evaluate the structural robustness quantitatively is one of the most challenging advanced problems in structural engineering.

bilingual.source: The structural design can decide that the structure the best proportion, and calculates the structural element which and the detailed material the construction needs.

bilingual.source: Polycarbonate is a kind of polymer, whose structural formula is line type.

yingyinNormal.en: Check the structural integrity of the trophy case, bitches, 'cause mama's bringing home some hardware!

yingyinNormal.en: So, the paddock is quite safe, then? We have the best structural engineers in the world. Yeah, so did Hammond.

yingyinNormal.en: That doesn't seem likely. Her bed's of sturdy construction. Even the addition of a second normal size human being wouldn't cause a structural failure, much less a homunculus such as yourself.
